entries.journal_entry_description: The Ewok Festival of Love celebrates romance, but not everyone has someone with whom to share their life. Help the romantically lost find love.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Find a match for your romance seeker companion. You'll find potential soul-mates for your companion in Tyrena on Corellia and in Kaadara on Naboo. If you need to summon your companion, you may do so from the Heart in your datapad.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to L-O53. You'll find him at the Ewok Festival of Love fountain in Tyrena on Corelia, Kaadara on Naboo, or the Sothern Ewok Lake Village on Endor..
